{"tid":2032524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方籲市民盡快逃往安全地方 將暴力執法 展示警方實力可接政治任務","createTime":"2020-05-24T06:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T06:26:14.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7cad758d942dec19b87a3eb17bf9c7a5fcb2b2","tid":2032524,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:12:34.000Z","msg":"警方籲市民盡快前往安全地方<br />\n24.05.2020 14:06<br />\n<br />\n警方指，下午約一時起，銅鑼灣有暴徒集結、襲擊警察，並向警察投擲硬物；軒尼詩道、怡和街及菲林明道等地均有暴徒以雜物堵路，多條行車線被阻塞。警方正在現場執法，使用最低所需武力，包括施放催淚煙。警方警告暴徒立即停止違法暴力行為，並呼籲市民盡快前往安全地方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289761&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289761%26csid%3D261_341&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=774c8638\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289761&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"ffb7ef7ef7aa20ff168d5be86813357e5d0736c2","tid":2032524,"uid":33874,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"警：唔好派武警取代我，我唔想失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb2e0f7976cfb6e420199842a72e5ff23222f9d","tid":2032524,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:17:14.000Z","msg":"暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15277f5be6288173b8bff516a179979bce14c05a","tid":2032524,"uid":49588,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:21:19.000Z","msg":"香港恐怖分子學話執法<br />\n<br />\n連證件都不敢展示於人<br />\n<br />\n真係笑撚死人"},{"pid":"f6b4e4c607223c55dfa9e0a65e0f68c20ddbe2e7","tid":2032524,"uid":168492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffb7ef7ef7aa20ff168d5be86813357e5d0736c2","tid":2032524,"uid":33874,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"警：唔好派武警取代我，我